      "text": [
        ": قال أبوعبدالله عليه السلام: إن الله عزوجل يقول: وَأَنَّ إِلَى رَبِّكَ الْمُنتَهَى فإذا انتهى الكلام إلى الله فأمسكوا"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "3. [3/373] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Yahya from Ahmad b. Muhammad from Ibn Abi Umayr from Abd al-Rahman b. al-Hajjaj from Sulayman b. Khalid who said: Abu Abdillah عليه السلام said: Allah Mighty and Majestic says: “and to your Lord is the End (finality)” <a href=\"/books/quran:53#h42\">[53:42]</a> so if your talks reach to Allah then remain silent."
        ]
